subject: Re: Dear beneficiary,
body:
Dear Sir,

Thank you for your message, yes we can give investment loans from USD
1000,000.00 to USD500,000,000.00 at 2% interest rate. you pay back after
one year or 5 years, no collateral is required.

REQUIREMENTS

1) Full name
2) Address
3) Company name
4) Area of Investment
5) Name of next kin , address and phone numbers
6) whatsapp and cell numbers.
7) Identification (International passport or driver's license).

Awaiting for your urgent response for the next level.

Sincerely,

Carey Edward/
